From 1b062d177bffa9cad551c8c1135acc3fbffcc596 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Claude <noreply@anthropic.com>
Date: Tue, 23 Jun 2026 23:55:33 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] fix(frontend): target AWS backend, transparent token refresh,
 correct error surfacing

- API base + same-origin proxy + Docker/cloudbuild now target https://api.synthos.dev
  (was the dead GCP Cloud Run URL); the deployed app was calling a backend that's gone
- client.ts: single-flight refresh on 401 with the rotating refresh token + retry, so
  sessions no longer drop every ~1h; surface backend error shape {error:{code,message}}
- auth-provider: persist and use refresh_token; refresh on expiry instead of logout
- remove dead GCP Workload-Identity proxy and the now-unused @vercel/oidc dependency
- remove duplicate root middleware.ts (src/middleware.ts with role guards is canonical)
- reconcile API client contracts (validations/warranties/admin/support/types) with the
  live backend response shapes
